Upgrade Ubuntu 18.04 Server to 22.04 LTS Server


sudo apt update && sudo apt upgrade

sudo apt dist-upgrade

sudo apt autoremove

sudo apt install update-manager-core

Edit the /etc/update-manager/release-upgrades file and make sure the value of Prompt is set to normal
Prompt=normal

sudo do-release-upgrade

sudo reboot

lsb_release -a
